maps/autumn/path-1.json/entities/302/set.text: Cette fois, je vais me rendre et prendre mes responsabilités pour mes crimes. Vraiment.

B... but I was going to come to you anyway.\. Don't you trust me?

maps/autumn/path-1.json/entities/302/set.orig: Sorry, pal.\. Trust is nice and all but I won't take any more risks with you.

maps/autumn/path-1.json/entities/302/set.orig: In any case, thanks, girl.\. You did great work here.\. Report back to the chief to get your reward.
